Interface CommandingMethod<T,M extends io.spine.type.MessageClass,E extends io.spine.core.MessageEnvelope<?,?,?>,R extends MethodResult>

public interface CommandingMethod<T,M extends io.spine.type.MessageClass,E extends io.spine.core.MessageEnvelope<?,?,?>,R extends MethodResult>
